WEBVTT

00:07.651 --> 00:08.791
Madam.

00:10.861 --> 00:14.311
There's nowhere to hide it.

00:14.931 --> 00:17.431
Yes. We can't hide it.

00:17.971 --> 00:18.970
Go.

00:18.971 --> 00:20.641
Paste it on for me.

00:21.021 --> 00:22.641
The more obvious it is, the better.

00:33.501 --> 00:34.641
Let's go.

01:15.181 --> 01:16.711
I remember now.

01:17.331 --> 01:19.401
Madam asked me to hide this

01:19.611 --> 01:20.911
for you.

01:23.961 --> 01:25.230
(His Majesty won't treat me
badly.)

01:25.231 --> 01:26.350
(The disaster is due to the seawall.)

01:26.351 --> 01:27.901
(Many are involved in this corruption.)

01:28.661 --> 01:30.241
What happened back then?

01:31.821 --> 01:33.071
This letter

01:34.211 --> 01:36.071
was written on a painting originally.

01:39.101 --> 01:40.241
Madam.

01:42.691 --> 01:43.831
Madam.

01:45.251 --> 01:46.391
Madam.

01:46.401 --> 01:48.311
You've received a letter
from the Duke of Ding.

01:53.121 --> 01:55.141
(To: Huisun, My Beloved Sister)

02:10.141 --> 02:12.831
My brother is playing this
hidden message game with me again.

02:15.021 --> 02:16.161
Get me a brush

02:16.371 --> 02:17.761
with some tea for me to dip in.

02:34.741 --> 02:35.951
Don't worry.

02:36.331 --> 02:38.671
His Majesty won't treat me
badly in the Capital City.

02:39.431 --> 02:42.161
The disaster caused by the hurricane
in Futing is due to the seawall.

02:42.371 --> 02:44.441
Many are involved in this corruption.

02:44.531 --> 02:47.041
I'll take this up to His Majesty.

02:50.801 --> 02:52.861
(Mu Chuan, Dou Shishu,
Song Yichun, Dou Shiying)

02:57.811 --> 02:58.700
Madam.

02:58.701 --> 03:00.071
Why did you cough up blood?

03:01.461 --> 03:02.601
Qi Xia.

03:02.861 --> 03:05.530
Dry this painting for me.

03:05.531 --> 03:06.810
Don't give it to anyone.

03:06.811 --> 03:08.391
Don't tell anybody about this.

03:08.491 --> 03:10.231
Except for Lord Song.

03:11.131 --> 03:12.020
Yes, Madam.

03:12.021 --> 03:13.161
Go now.

03:17.531 --> 03:18.791
Where should I hide it?

03:19.261 --> 03:20.370
Madam.

03:20.371 --> 03:21.721
Where should I hide it?

03:26.021 --> 03:27.561
There's nowhere to hide it.

03:28.061 --> 03:29.201
Qi Xia.

03:32.091 --> 03:33.561
Paste it on for me.

03:34.771 --> 03:36.831
The more obvious it is, the better.

03:37.371 --> 03:38.561
Don't worry, Madam.

03:38.611 --> 03:40.330
I'll hand it over to Lord Song.

03:40.331 --> 03:41.471
Go now.

03:41.581 --> 03:42.721
Okay.

04:12.901 --> 04:14.041
Father.

04:14.531 --> 04:16.441
How can you do this?

04:17.211 --> 04:18.460
She is my mother.

04:18.461 --> 04:20.241
She is not your mother.

04:20.501 --> 04:21.500
Me, you and Shuyao

04:21.501 --> 04:24.001
are the true family.

04:24.851 --> 04:25.730
Now,

04:25.731 --> 04:28.380
your mother has suffered
so many years because of me.

04:28.381 --> 04:30.151
I don't want to let her suffer anymore.

05:38.561 --> 05:40.541
(Song Yichun, Dou Shiying)

05:52.211 --> 05:53.951
We know the truth now.

05:55.331 --> 05:57.121
With this list in our hands,

05:57.581 --> 05:59.591
Lord Qing's life is in our hands too.

05:59.651 --> 06:01.530
He touched the foundation
of the country.

06:01.531 --> 06:02.921
We have solid evidence against him.

06:05.851 --> 06:07.441
His Majesty is a wise emperor.

06:07.461 --> 06:09.591
His Majesty is in failing health.

06:09.901 --> 06:12.441
Will he end up like the Duke of Ding?

06:13.141 --> 06:15.060
Besides, too many people
are involved in this.

06:15.061 --> 06:16.681
We don't know how it'll turn out.

06:18.141 --> 06:20.681
Why is my father's name on this list?

06:21.581 --> 06:23.761
My Fifth Uncle
is Lord Qing's accomplice.

06:24.941 --> 06:28.471
Is he trying to drag
my father down with him?

07:51.921 --> 07:56.120
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

07:56.121 --> 07:59.200
=Episode 31=

07:59.201 --> 08:01.040
(Dou's Residence)

08:01.041 --> 08:02.321
Why are you back?

08:02.501 --> 08:03.881
Why didn't you tell me in advance?

08:05.061 --> 08:06.060
Wait.

08:06.061 --> 08:06.940
Gao Sheng.

08:06.941 --> 08:09.101
Make a pot of tea
with my newly acquired Longjing tea.

08:09.331 --> 08:10.170
Yes, Master.

08:10.171 --> 08:11.290
Leave us.

08:11.291 --> 08:12.431
No need to serve us.

08:15.641 --> 08:17.561
I have things to tell you too.

08:17.761 --> 08:18.901
Gao Sheng.

08:25.541 --> 08:26.681
Seventh Master.

08:30.441 --> 08:33.981
(Buyer: Dou Shiying)

08:36.531 --> 08:37.671
Father.

08:37.751 --> 08:39.220
The mansions that you are looking at

08:39.221 --> 08:40.521
are quite costly.

08:40.621 --> 08:41.850
I bought these mansions

08:41.851 --> 08:44.591
as safety nets for you.

08:44.741 --> 08:47.041
Not long ago, I got some extra money.

08:47.171 --> 08:49.521
I invested in the Capital's
new Yunfei Silverhouse.

08:49.621 --> 08:51.231
Their profit margin is amazing.

08:51.451 --> 08:54.310
Using the profit from Yunfei Silverhouse
to pay for the house installment

08:54.311 --> 08:55.451
is just nice.

08:55.811 --> 08:57.530
I know all the jewelers

08:57.531 --> 08:58.671
in the capital.

08:58.771 --> 09:00.801
Why have I never heard
about Yunfei Silverhouse?

09:03.931 --> 09:04.860
Father.

09:04.861 --> 09:07.231
You are a naive and easily swayed man.

09:07.451 --> 09:08.831
Don't simply invest in something.

09:09.501 --> 09:11.201
I don't want you
to lose all your savings

09:11.381 --> 09:13.031
for some meager profits.

09:13.901 --> 09:16.390
I'm at the Ministry
of Revenue after all.

09:16.391 --> 09:17.900
I've looked at their accounts.

09:17.901 --> 09:20.441
The Silverhouse has great craftsmanship.

09:20.651 --> 09:22.081
It has many customers.

09:22.091 --> 09:23.650
Official Mu introduced us to that shop.

09:23.651 --> 09:25.481
Shishu and I have invested
some money into it.

09:25.491 --> 09:26.561
It's a profitable business.

09:34.101 --> 09:35.241
Lord Song.

09:35.261 --> 09:36.530
I've found out about everything.

09:36.531 --> 09:37.991
The one who's running the Silverhouse

09:38.001 --> 09:39.991
is the Duke of Jing's family,
the Zhang family.

09:41.901 --> 09:43.071
Who else

09:43.221 --> 09:45.231
in the capital has invested in it?

09:45.501 --> 09:47.711
The staff there refuses
to reveal anything.

09:47.831 --> 09:48.980
I've asked the people around.

09:48.981 --> 09:50.201
Those who visit the place

09:50.281 --> 09:52.801
are mostly high-ranking
ministers and officials.

09:54.221 --> 09:55.871
The Zhang family is wealthy.

09:55.881 --> 09:58.481
They spent tens of thousands of taels
just to renovate their yard.

09:58.491 --> 09:59.680
With him running the place,

09:59.681 --> 10:01.450
I'm sure it's safe since many of us

10:01.451 --> 10:02.801
are the investors too.

10:04.651 --> 10:06.041
You are at the Ministry of Revenue.

10:06.221 --> 10:08.681
I'm sure you know the condition
of the court right now.

10:08.811 --> 10:11.100
The annual tax revenue
is three million taels of silver.

10:11.101 --> 10:13.111
But the expenditure
is six million taels of silver.

10:13.381 --> 10:14.530
The court is losing money

10:14.531 --> 10:16.161
and the people are having a hard time.

10:16.171 --> 10:19.081
So, how could the Zhang family spend
tens of thousands of taels so easily?

10:19.421 --> 10:20.930
What's the salary of the Duke of Jing?

10:20.931 --> 10:23.471
What makes them so wealthy?

10:27.921 --> 10:29.281
Maybe

10:29.771 --> 10:31.591
he has some side businesses going on.

10:32.171 --> 10:33.871
He's making money with money.

10:34.301 --> 10:36.231
Public and private money

10:36.341 --> 10:37.620
are different.

10:37.621 --> 10:38.761
Father.

10:38.861 --> 10:40.801
The Zhang family
is Her Majesty's birth family.

10:41.021 --> 10:43.171
Their family comes from
the horse market in Liaodong.

10:43.291 --> 10:45.470
Lord Qing and His Highness
are against each other now.

10:45.471 --> 10:48.171
They are using those profits
to bring those ministers to their side.

10:50.021 --> 10:52.801
How can you put them together?

10:52.901 --> 10:54.231
Business is business.

10:54.451 --> 10:56.041
The court is the court.

10:56.051 --> 10:58.591
The Duke of Jing has never
cared about political matters.

11:00.381 --> 11:03.041
Do you really think
that they are not related?

11:03.981 --> 11:05.121
Let me ask you.

11:05.411 --> 11:08.871
Did you sign your name when you invested

11:08.981 --> 11:10.161
in the Silverhouse?

11:19.811 --> 11:22.281
It's very clear that Lord Qing
is going to fight for the crown.

11:22.691 --> 11:23.900
By signing a contract with him,

11:23.901 --> 11:25.681
you are bound to him now.

11:26.051 --> 11:27.951
No matter what he does in the future,

11:28.141 --> 11:29.351
you can only support him

11:29.931 --> 11:32.801
or act ignorance.

11:33.641 --> 11:35.111
I'm not trying to gang up with anyone.

11:36.021 --> 11:38.050
Fifth Uncle is already
a member of their gang.

11:38.051 --> 11:39.451
That's why he dragged you into this.

11:39.461 --> 11:41.281
He wants to use
your relationship with Yantang

11:41.291 --> 11:42.191
to drag him down too

11:42.201 --> 11:43.761
by forcing him to follow their orders.

11:48.341 --> 11:50.671
Fighting for the crown
and forming gangs.

11:50.681 --> 11:53.351
Our entire family will be in danger
if we are tied to these matters.

11:53.381 --> 11:54.521
No.

11:54.981 --> 11:56.351
I need to get out of this business.

11:57.861 --> 11:58.810
Father.

11:58.811 --> 12:00.071
Let me do it for you.

12:00.291 --> 12:01.751
I'll go to the Silverhouse now.

12:02.451 --> 12:03.591
Ms. Longevity.

12:09.571 --> 12:10.420
Yantang.

12:10.421 --> 12:11.831
What should we do now?

12:12.291 --> 12:14.161
How about I take a leave

12:14.691 --> 12:15.951
or resign?

12:16.811 --> 12:17.951
Father-in-law.

12:18.291 --> 12:19.521
Even if you resign,

12:19.651 --> 12:21.591
you'll still be Ms. Longevity's father

12:21.771 --> 12:23.351
and my father-in-law.

12:24.691 --> 12:27.751
I promised Ms. Longevity
that I'll protect her family.

12:28.341 --> 12:29.711
Their target is me.

12:30.141 --> 12:31.281
I'll take care of this.

12:33.051 --> 12:34.191
Summon the secret guards.

12:34.571 --> 12:35.711
Your Lordship.

12:36.931 --> 12:39.281
Lord Qing and the others
are investigating our men now.

12:39.511 --> 12:42.071
What if they trap us all?

12:44.041 --> 12:46.761
If he really wants to set up traps
in the Capital City,

12:46.771 --> 12:48.751
he can never control who's the hunter

12:49.741 --> 12:51.521
and who's the prey.

13:01.021 --> 13:02.201
Secret guards?

13:09.241 --> 13:11.781
(Yunfei Silverhouse)

13:11.851 --> 13:12.740
Mr. Wang.

13:12.741 --> 13:14.100
- Welcome.
- Okay.

13:14.101 --> 13:15.281
- Welcome.
- Come.

13:15.641 --> 13:16.720
Come.

13:16.721 --> 13:17.861
Take care.

13:24.931 --> 13:26.281
Duchess of Ying.

13:26.651 --> 13:29.650
Our Ladyship is here
to propose a business to your owner.

13:29.651 --> 13:31.281
Please notify Madam Wei about it.

13:33.411 --> 13:35.170
I'm an impatient woman
with a bad temper.

13:35.171 --> 13:36.591
She better come here quickly.

13:36.981 --> 13:40.001
Otherwise, if I make a scene here,

13:40.051 --> 13:42.831
it'll affect your business.

13:45.691 --> 13:47.591
I'll inform our owner
about it right away.

13:47.771 --> 13:49.041
Feel free to shop around.

13:54.231 --> 13:55.871
Take a look.

14:12.621 --> 14:13.761
Your Ladyship.

14:15.171 --> 14:16.641
Please follow me.

14:21.011 --> 14:22.570
I'll pay ten times
the price of the capital

14:22.571 --> 14:24.281
that my father invested
plus the interest.

14:24.291 --> 14:26.781
We can negotiate on the customer base
of the Miao family's shop

14:26.791 --> 14:28.871
as well as the craftsmen
of the Zhaowen Bookstore.

14:29.021 --> 14:30.871
In exchange for the contract
my father signed.

14:31.771 --> 14:34.201
I would like to terminate it.

14:35.981 --> 14:37.161
This is

14:37.501 --> 14:40.111
like a windfall deal for you, right?

14:40.771 --> 14:41.991
Your Ladyship.

14:42.161 --> 14:43.831
According to the rules
of the Silverhouse,

14:43.901 --> 14:45.161
once the contract is signed,

14:45.261 --> 14:46.810
you can't terminate it

14:46.811 --> 14:48.641
regardless of the profit and loss.

14:49.261 --> 14:51.351
So, the rules of the Silverhouse

14:51.501 --> 14:53.401
is stricter than the law of the country.

14:54.021 --> 14:55.591
You call it an investment.

14:55.691 --> 14:58.591
But it sounds like selling yourself.

14:59.411 --> 15:01.071
Madam Wei has always put profit first.

15:01.171 --> 15:02.751
But you've changed out of the blue.

15:02.901 --> 15:05.530
Looks like the illegal benefits
that the Silverhouse is making

15:05.531 --> 15:07.591
is more than what I can offer.

15:09.221 --> 15:11.441
How dare you say that?

15:12.101 --> 15:13.570
What benefits have the ladies

15:13.571 --> 15:15.591
of the Dou family ever given us?

15:16.381 --> 15:20.751
You just continue to feed
on the Wei family

15:20.901 --> 15:23.071
and destroy us.

15:24.261 --> 15:26.860
Your father and your uncle are lucky

15:26.861 --> 15:29.071
that we've allowed them to invest in us.

15:29.861 --> 15:31.751
How dare you feel so emboldened to think

15:31.861 --> 15:34.641
that you can terminate the contract
on behalf of your father and uncle?

15:35.221 --> 15:37.321
Go ahead and cause a scene here.

15:37.571 --> 15:38.951
I don't believe

15:39.691 --> 15:43.521
that the Shengtian Prison
will get you off the hook.

15:44.051 --> 15:45.201
Wei Tingzhen.

15:45.901 --> 15:47.681
I've tried to be courteous first.

15:48.141 --> 15:49.871
I've shown you some respect today.

15:50.051 --> 15:51.401
In the future,

15:52.021 --> 15:53.691
you won't be receiving
the same treatment.

15:55.621 --> 15:56.801
In the future?

15:57.021 --> 15:59.171
In the future,
when someone else takes over the crown,

15:59.221 --> 16:00.471
you and your husband

16:00.691 --> 16:01.980
will perish.

16:01.981 --> 16:04.351
How can you disrespect me then?

16:21.041 --> 16:23.510
(Official Letter,
Commander of the Shadow Guard)

16:23.511 --> 16:26.021
(To be opened at
the Northern Pacification Bureau Hall)

16:26.171 --> 16:28.500
They say that it's hard to break
the addiction to gambling.

16:28.501 --> 16:30.951
Why do you think it's like that?

16:34.931 --> 16:36.161
Once someone

16:36.901 --> 16:39.170
has experienced the feeling
of earning money tenfold

16:39.171 --> 16:40.740
and becoming a wealthy person overnight,

16:40.741 --> 16:41.951
that thrill

16:42.171 --> 16:44.801
is something they can't forget
even at the cost of their fingers.

16:46.021 --> 16:48.471
That's what happening
at Lord Qing's gambling table.

16:48.771 --> 16:51.281
You can loan money and
pay them back with interest.

16:51.341 --> 16:52.641
The more you gamble,

16:53.221 --> 16:54.681
the more money you can make.

16:58.211 --> 16:59.921
I've quit gambling
since a long time ago.

17:01.261 --> 17:02.641
I'm afraid

17:03.291 --> 17:04.681
that I can't accept your gift.

17:04.901 --> 17:05.661
Sure.

17:05.671 --> 17:07.811
Something has been stolen
from His Highness's residence today.

17:07.821 --> 17:09.311
And the culprit is caught red-handed.

17:10.251 --> 17:11.751
What should we do now?

17:13.001 --> 17:14.170
Lord Qing has written a letter

17:14.171 --> 17:16.751
to recommend you
as the Pacification envoy.

17:17.251 --> 17:19.161
Will Song Mo save you?

17:19.491 --> 17:21.081
Even if you are not willing to join us,

17:21.251 --> 17:22.471
there will be more

17:23.251 --> 17:24.511
who are willing.

17:27.341 --> 17:28.481
Another thing,

17:30.411 --> 17:32.441
don't forget about Miss Zhao.

17:38.251 --> 17:40.410
Dou Shishu asked Zou Er to deliver
an invitation card

17:40.411 --> 17:41.581
to meet you at the Silverhouse

17:41.591 --> 17:43.100
at midnight tomorrow to discuss

17:43.101 --> 17:44.650
about the business contract.

17:44.651 --> 17:46.791
Our men are ready.

17:47.621 --> 17:49.551
Dou Shishu is a ruthless

17:49.731 --> 17:51.031
and selfish man.

17:51.101 --> 17:52.650
He won't hand over the signed contract

17:52.651 --> 17:54.951
unless you pledge your loyalty to him.

17:55.251 --> 17:56.380
You should stay away

17:56.381 --> 17:57.881
from this treacherous banquet.

17:58.341 --> 18:00.620
Wait until we find
what's behind the Silverhouse.

18:00.621 --> 18:01.761
No.

18:02.491 --> 18:05.401
Lord Qing has already made his stand
during the martial arts competition.

18:05.651 --> 18:07.441
He won't give me time to drag this out.

18:08.211 --> 18:09.441
Haven't you realised?

18:09.581 --> 18:12.401
Official Lu's visit has gotten
far and few lately.

18:14.251 --> 18:17.161
Other than taking care of you,

18:17.581 --> 18:19.361
Official Lu is only in charge
of His Majesty.

18:19.971 --> 18:22.751
Has His Majesty's illness worsened?

18:22.901 --> 18:24.201
The arrow has been nocked.

18:24.691 --> 18:27.641
If I can't become Lord Qing's blade,

18:28.141 --> 18:30.441
I'll become a thorn
that he has to get rid of.

18:35.011 --> 18:36.170
- Your Ladyship.
- Your Ladyship.

18:36.171 --> 18:37.791
Did you manage to retrieve the contract?

18:37.861 --> 18:40.441
I've gotten something
that may be even better than that.

18:42.251 --> 18:44.881
Our weakness is their flaw.

18:47.301 --> 18:49.551
The stars have gone to sleep
behind the clouds.

18:50.101 --> 18:51.841
Time to rest.

18:52.011 --> 18:53.690
Midnight has arrived.

18:53.691 --> 18:54.930
Time to close your shops.

18:54.931 --> 18:56.071
Hurry up.

18:58.191 --> 18:59.951
I never thought that I would be

19:00.391 --> 19:03.641
welcomed personally
by Official Dou one day.

19:04.051 --> 19:05.741
I thought you wouldn't be here.

19:06.321 --> 19:09.451
Looks like you really care
about my brother.

19:09.781 --> 19:13.441
Unfortunately, the way
we care about him is different.

19:16.011 --> 19:17.201
Please, a moment.

19:17.381 --> 19:19.031
We do business here.

19:19.101 --> 19:21.711
I need to protect our jewelry here.

19:22.341 --> 19:25.161
Please leave your weapons at the door.

19:26.011 --> 19:27.401
He has received special permission

19:27.491 --> 19:30.511
from His Majesty to carry
his sword at all times.

19:32.111 --> 19:34.161
If you think of me as an enemy,

19:34.471 --> 19:36.721
there's no need for us
to meet each other here.

19:37.251 --> 19:38.930
This is an important family matter.

19:38.931 --> 19:41.031
I just want to meet you alone

19:41.451 --> 19:42.921
and drink some tea.

19:47.301 --> 19:48.140
Wait for me outside.

19:48.141 --> 19:49.281
Yes.

20:01.141 --> 20:02.841
You've been avoiding me.

20:03.381 --> 20:05.551
So, I have no choice
but to trick you here.

20:06.691 --> 20:08.031
Don't blame Official Dou.

20:13.601 --> 20:15.891
This is the path that Official Dou
has chosen for himself.

20:17.931 --> 20:19.271
Why should I blame him?

20:21.781 --> 20:23.791
I really have the snow lingzhi.

20:24.011 --> 20:25.601
After your poison has been neutralized,

20:25.691 --> 20:28.161
you can live a long life
with your wife and your children.

20:28.301 --> 20:30.531
In the future, we can have
the brain from the Dou family

20:30.541 --> 20:31.951
and the brawn from the Duke of Ying.

20:32.171 --> 20:33.641
And the country can be at peace.

20:33.971 --> 20:35.311
Isn't that great?

20:36.101 --> 20:37.321
If I neutralize my poison,

20:37.941 --> 20:39.441
I can't neutralize my grudge.

20:41.671 --> 20:42.970
Across history,

20:42.971 --> 20:44.711
many sacrifices had to be made

20:44.851 --> 20:46.441
before a wise emperor could be crowned.

20:47.661 --> 20:49.171
It's just a path that has to be taken.

20:49.821 --> 20:51.121
It's not a destination.

20:52.141 --> 20:54.161
If it's because of your mother,

20:55.211 --> 20:57.100
I can give you Song Han's head

20:57.101 --> 20:59.161
tomorrow to show

20:59.491 --> 21:00.951
my sincerity.

21:10.301 --> 21:12.681
Your uncle halted my plan.

21:13.451 --> 21:16.031
It's true that Mother and I
intend to eliminate him.

21:16.041 --> 21:18.121
However, the Duke of Ding
was a meritorious general.

21:18.581 --> 21:19.620
If nothing had occurred

21:19.621 --> 21:21.361
between him and Father,

21:21.691 --> 21:23.791
he wouldn't have ended up this way.

21:25.861 --> 21:28.921
He died because of his blind loyalty.

21:29.541 --> 21:31.140
Shouldn't his departed soul

21:31.141 --> 21:32.751
resent Wang Ge,

21:32.861 --> 21:34.921
me, or Mother?

21:35.341 --> 21:37.711
The twelve imperial gold decrees
that summoned Yue Fei back

21:38.451 --> 21:39.711
were issued by Zhao Gou,

21:40.861 --> 21:42.271
not Qin Hui.

21:44.381 --> 21:45.521
Yes.

21:46.211 --> 21:47.441
In front of Yue Fei's statue,

21:48.141 --> 21:51.161
Zhao Gou should kneel
and accept criticism.

21:51.781 --> 21:55.791
Even so, Qin Hui would never
be able to stand up again.

22:00.651 --> 22:01.791
Song Mo,

22:02.691 --> 22:05.401
His Highness has given you
enough respect.

22:05.731 --> 22:07.271
If you still continue to defy him,

22:07.411 --> 22:09.620
you'll die here tonight

22:09.621 --> 22:10.881
for assassinating Lord Qing.

22:11.061 --> 22:12.881
And Ms. Longevity will become a widow.

22:13.621 --> 22:16.161
Can you still take your revenge?

22:17.691 --> 22:21.401
Your Highness, you're good
at manipulating people.

22:22.861 --> 22:24.001
However,

22:24.781 --> 22:26.121
wise men

22:27.211 --> 22:29.951
tend to fall into their own traps.

22:37.821 --> 22:39.140
I told you before,

22:39.141 --> 22:40.751
your army is weak.

22:42.251 --> 22:43.441
Song Mo, how dare you

22:43.491 --> 22:44.541
attempt to murder a prince!

22:44.551 --> 22:45.620
Do you know
what punishment you will face?

22:45.621 --> 22:47.501
If my revenge
were only about taking his life,

22:47.971 --> 22:50.081
I could succeed tonight.

22:50.101 --> 22:51.241
Don't forget

22:51.311 --> 22:52.620
you came here for the agreement.

22:52.621 --> 22:53.841
You forgot that,

22:54.581 --> 22:55.881
not me.

23:04.341 --> 23:05.481
Don't worry.

23:05.621 --> 23:07.551
The agreement
in the secret chamber downstairs

23:08.011 --> 23:10.271
will remain intact.

23:15.411 --> 23:16.601
I measured it.

23:17.061 --> 23:20.231
The main hall is sixteen steps long
and twelve steps wide.

23:20.491 --> 23:21.751
There are three rooms inside

23:22.141 --> 23:23.601
with six pillars.

23:24.101 --> 23:25.361
I confirmed

23:25.781 --> 23:28.311
the difference between the interior
and exterior is one zhang.

23:28.901 --> 23:30.601
There must be a secret chamber.

23:35.411 --> 23:36.780
When you confront Lord Qing,

23:36.781 --> 23:38.401
I'll blow open the outer wall

23:38.451 --> 23:39.641
and retrieve the agreement.

23:42.581 --> 23:43.640
Your Highness!

23:43.641 --> 23:45.621
(Silver Ornament Store)

23:47.861 --> 23:49.001
Your Lordship,

23:49.781 --> 23:51.471
all the agreements are here.

23:52.491 --> 23:53.681
Well done.

24:01.491 --> 24:03.270
Song Mo is insane.

24:03.271 --> 24:04.900
He set off gunpowder in the street

24:04.901 --> 24:06.231
and endangered the people's lives.

24:06.451 --> 24:07.751
He must be executed immediately.

24:10.541 --> 24:11.991
I will hand over all of this

24:12.141 --> 24:13.820
and the Duke of Ding's letter

24:13.821 --> 24:15.791
to His Majesty.

24:16.581 --> 24:18.441
What do you think His Majesty

24:18.781 --> 24:20.951
will decide about your crime
of fraternizing?

24:22.381 --> 24:24.361
Jiang Meisun owned a troop
in the southeast,

24:24.581 --> 24:26.601
and you intended to blow up the capital.

24:26.621 --> 24:28.401
Everyone bears witness tonight.

24:28.541 --> 24:29.921
The Jiang family

24:30.381 --> 24:31.681
is no longer loyalists.

24:32.341 --> 24:34.361
You don't deserve
to mention the Jiang family.

24:38.731 --> 24:39.871
Your Lordship.

24:42.821 --> 24:44.711
Song Mo attempted to assassinate me.

24:45.971 --> 24:47.121
Whoever kills him

24:47.541 --> 24:48.751
will earn the greatest reward.

24:50.551 --> 24:51.691
Hold up!

24:53.341 --> 24:54.481
Make way.

24:55.321 --> 24:56.461
Stay still.

25:05.401 --> 25:06.541
Yantang.

25:07.901 --> 25:09.041
Why are you here?

25:13.621 --> 25:18.200
Lord Qing, Duke of Ying,
and Official Dou,

25:18.201 --> 25:21.471
please come with me to the palace.

25:21.591 --> 25:22.991
Are you blind?

25:23.001 --> 25:24.970
Song Mo set fire
and attempted to assassinate me.

25:24.971 --> 25:26.121
He should be executed.

25:26.491 --> 25:27.971
This evil woman plotted against me.

25:28.131 --> 25:29.551
She deserves no better.

25:33.541 --> 25:35.681
Yantang.

25:38.061 --> 25:39.210
Finally, I've found

25:39.211 --> 25:41.121
your weakness.

25:42.781 --> 25:45.300
I only follow the imperial decree.

25:45.301 --> 25:47.551
Please don't blame me, Your Highness.

26:00.101 --> 26:02.551
People said it's inauspicious
for pregnant women to see blood.

26:04.651 --> 26:06.201
You shouldn't have come.

26:11.301 --> 26:13.121
Didn't we agree

26:14.491 --> 26:16.401
to face everything together,

26:17.381 --> 26:18.951
no matter what happened?

26:22.621 --> 26:24.081
I'll enter the palace with you.

26:25.681 --> 26:31.381
(Qianqing Palace)

26:38.721 --> 26:41.170
(Intermediary: Wei Tingzhen, Proposer)

26:41.171 --> 26:42.571
Father, please investigate wisely.

26:42.581 --> 26:44.681
Song Mo deliberately set a trap
and started the fire.

26:44.691 --> 26:46.511
If I hadn't defended myself,

26:46.691 --> 26:48.791
I might not have survived
to meet you now.

26:50.651 --> 26:53.751
Is that something a prince should say?

26:55.541 --> 26:56.681
Your Majesty,

26:56.691 --> 26:58.711
(Revere Heaven and Ancestral Wisdom)
Lord Qing formed a faction,

26:59.061 --> 27:00.401
embezzled massive funds,

27:00.541 --> 27:02.140
and fraternized with important officials

27:02.141 --> 27:03.641
under the name of Silverhouse
in the capital.

27:03.651 --> 27:06.311
They committed bureaucratic corruption
and exploited the people.

27:06.581 --> 27:09.311
The list of his fraction
and the agreement are here.

27:09.621 --> 27:11.271
Please make your judgment, Your Majesty.

27:12.821 --> 27:14.471
Are the important officials
you mentioned

27:14.781 --> 27:16.250
those who impeached the Crown Prince

27:16.251 --> 27:18.441
a couple of days ago?

27:19.341 --> 27:21.991
You instigated me to fight
against my brother

27:22.101 --> 27:24.121
for your own vengeance, didn't you?

27:24.651 --> 27:25.881
Words may be fabricated,

27:26.171 --> 27:28.271
but signatures and thumbprints can't.

27:28.341 --> 27:30.340
Over a million silver taels
in this ledger

27:30.341 --> 27:32.271
can be tracked as clear as day.

27:32.821 --> 27:36.841
I request a thorough investigation
into every residence involved.

27:39.101 --> 27:40.241
Your Majesty.

27:41.491 --> 27:42.681
Duke of Ying,

27:43.381 --> 27:45.140
this incident involves many parties.

27:45.141 --> 27:47.921
His Majesty is exhausted now.

27:48.451 --> 27:49.591
Your Majesty.

27:49.861 --> 27:51.001
Your Majesty.

27:52.581 --> 27:54.781
Lord Yu'an, Lord Jihuai,
and Duke of Qing

27:54.782 --> 27:55.881
request an audience.

28:06.851 --> 28:08.661
All the lords are inside.

28:09.261 --> 28:12.441
Even the key ministers

28:12.781 --> 28:14.361
intend to impeach Song Mo.

28:14.971 --> 28:16.511
He sent himself to his demise.

28:17.491 --> 28:19.641
Do you want to follow him as well?

28:22.451 --> 28:23.881
You blew up

28:24.971 --> 28:26.791
the secret chamber, didn't you?

28:27.001 --> 28:29.481
Do you know the punishment
for illegal explosive manufacturing?

28:29.491 --> 28:30.391
Capital crime.

28:31.301 --> 28:33.471
However, Fifth Uncle,
you're in charge of the military,

28:33.691 --> 28:35.471
and your niece secretly made explosives.

28:36.011 --> 28:38.031
You made this happen.

28:38.141 --> 28:39.901
- You!
- By then,

28:39.902 --> 28:41.231
will the Empress and Lord Qing

28:41.411 --> 28:42.751
sacrifice you

28:43.411 --> 28:45.511
to die with me and Song Mo?

28:45.581 --> 28:48.121
You... You're so despicable.

28:48.511 --> 28:50.571
Are you trying to drag
the Dou family down with you?

28:50.581 --> 28:51.791
I'm protecting the Dou family.

28:52.171 --> 28:53.620
Lord Qing embezzled national funds,

28:53.621 --> 28:54.881
and the evidence is conclusive.

28:59.171 --> 29:00.471
His Majesty is a wise ruler.

29:00.931 --> 29:02.921
Besides, this incident
has startled many parties.

29:03.731 --> 29:05.511
His Majesty must make a decision.

29:06.301 --> 29:08.751
Madam Dou, you may be good
at managing household affairs,

29:09.341 --> 29:12.551
but you underestimate
the court politics.

29:17.211 --> 29:18.551
You must be tired, Official Dou.

29:18.781 --> 29:19.820
Go take a rest.

29:19.821 --> 29:21.031
Yes, Your Highness.

29:23.171 --> 29:25.361
You'll become a mother soon.

29:25.971 --> 29:27.921
You should understand how parents think.

29:29.301 --> 29:30.991
Even though Song Mo
has a rightful reason,

29:31.011 --> 29:32.471
he's still an official.

29:33.411 --> 29:35.780
Youting may have committed
a grave mistake,

29:35.781 --> 29:38.201
but he's His Majesty's son.

29:38.821 --> 29:41.201
His Majesty isn't just
Lord Qing's father,

29:41.931 --> 29:44.031
he's the father of this nation.

29:44.101 --> 29:45.010
All the more reason

29:45.011 --> 29:47.161
he should consider the bigger picture.

29:47.581 --> 29:50.010
If every official who commits corruption

29:50.011 --> 29:51.250
were executed,

29:51.251 --> 29:53.081
how would the imperial court operate?

29:53.171 --> 29:55.441
Would the people still have faith in it?

29:56.181 --> 29:57.811
The law doesn't punish
when too many people are guilty,

29:57.821 --> 29:59.121
let alone their own families.

29:59.341 --> 30:01.991
Lord Yu'an is His Majesty's uncle,

30:02.211 --> 30:04.791
and Lord Jihuai is his blood brother.

30:05.491 --> 30:07.641
The agreement might not serve as proof,

30:09.011 --> 30:10.540
but it's definitely a giant stone

30:10.541 --> 30:12.401
to crush you.

30:15.861 --> 30:18.450
Song Mo was just promoted to the Command
of Military Command,

30:19.321 --> 30:21.751
yet he exploded the Silverhouse
and committed theft.

30:22.011 --> 30:23.730
You command the Imperial Guard,

30:23.731 --> 30:25.641
yet you assault a prince in public.

30:25.821 --> 30:28.031
(Lord Yu'an, Lord Jihuai)
How arrogant of you.

30:28.101 --> 30:29.551
You've disgraced the imperial favor.

30:29.691 --> 30:32.641
You must be punished severely
to quell public wrath.

30:32.971 --> 30:34.231
According to the law,

30:34.351 --> 30:36.591
royal family members must not interfere
in court affairs.

30:37.251 --> 30:38.730
I failed my duty and committed arson.

30:38.731 --> 30:40.401
I admit it.

30:40.901 --> 30:44.441
But if your name appears
on the agreement,

30:45.061 --> 30:48.201
will you admit it or not?

30:52.251 --> 30:54.811
Your Majesty, the founding emperor left us
ancestral teachings.

30:54.821 --> 30:56.801
If the family is at peace,
the nation will be stable.

30:56.811 --> 30:58.721
The royal family is a role model
for the people.

30:58.731 --> 31:00.361
Filial piety is the main principle
in governance.

31:00.381 --> 31:03.121
Familial suspicions and brotherly discord
are the greatest taboos.

31:03.581 --> 31:05.081
As an official,

31:05.331 --> 31:07.340
he instigated disharmony
within the royal family.

31:07.341 --> 31:09.081
He deserves a million deaths.

31:09.411 --> 31:12.371
It was I who held your hand

31:12.381 --> 31:15.210
as you transcribed every single sentence
of the ancestral teachings.

31:15.211 --> 31:16.351
Your Majesty,

31:16.691 --> 31:17.831
have you forgotten?

31:18.061 --> 31:19.580
Song Mo's accusation

31:19.581 --> 31:22.250
is merely an attempt
to absolve his family's crimes.

31:22.251 --> 31:23.711
Your Majesty, you're wise.

31:23.781 --> 31:26.401
You must be able to discern
his base intention.

31:26.411 --> 31:28.661
- Your Majesty, please decide wisely.
- Your Majesty, please decide wisely.

31:43.041 --> 31:44.921
This agreement

31:46.861 --> 31:48.471
is stained with blood.

31:53.411 --> 31:55.201
I can't read it clearly.

32:09.541 --> 32:10.820
You've been kneeling until now.

32:10.821 --> 32:12.980
You've done more than enough as a wife.

32:12.981 --> 32:14.711
You should consider yourself.

32:15.251 --> 32:17.921
Divorce Song Mo
and return to the Dou family.

32:18.141 --> 32:21.401
Your fifth uncle can
keep your family safe,

32:21.541 --> 32:22.970
and I'll keep a position

32:22.971 --> 32:24.401
for you.

32:24.821 --> 32:27.161
Becoming the wife of a guilty official

32:27.301 --> 32:29.311
or a noble lady

32:30.141 --> 32:31.441
is an easy choice.

32:34.411 --> 32:35.551
Who I choose to be

32:36.901 --> 32:39.031
isn't about whose wife I am

32:39.731 --> 32:41.121
or daughter I am.

32:42.061 --> 32:44.121
It depends on who I am.

32:44.861 --> 32:47.361
A person with integrity
walks their own path.

32:48.971 --> 32:51.881
I'll be waiting here
until Song Mo comes out.

32:55.581 --> 32:57.601
The path of a ruler
and the path of an official

32:57.621 --> 32:59.511
are different.

32:59.821 --> 33:01.380
If Song Mo were to leave here

33:01.381 --> 33:02.250
with a clear name,

33:02.251 --> 33:03.441
there would only be one path.

33:03.901 --> 33:05.681
That's to admit
that his actions tonight

33:05.861 --> 33:07.690
were ordered by his father-in-law

33:07.691 --> 33:10.601
and placed all the blame on Dou Shiying.

33:14.171 --> 33:15.711
On this agreement,

33:17.001 --> 33:18.360
I can only recognize

33:18.361 --> 33:20.511
Dou Shiying's name.

33:21.821 --> 33:24.361
You went to Yunfei Silverhouse
for him, didn't you?

33:24.721 --> 33:26.320
He must've become dotard

33:26.321 --> 33:29.941
and driven you and Youting apart.

33:32.411 --> 33:35.401
I barged into Yunfei Silverhouse
and started the fire.

33:35.691 --> 33:37.401
Father-in-law has no idea about it.

33:38.301 --> 33:39.471
If you want to punish someone,

33:39.621 --> 33:40.951
please punish me alone.

33:41.901 --> 33:44.580
It has nothing to do with others.

33:44.581 --> 33:45.721
Song Mo!

33:47.821 --> 33:48.961
Your Majesty.

33:49.491 --> 33:52.921
His Majesty cherish your talent.

33:53.061 --> 33:55.681
Please don't be stubborn
and take the blame.

33:55.971 --> 33:57.900
Your future will be wasted.

33:57.901 --> 33:58.970
Your Majesty,

33:58.971 --> 34:00.361
given Song Mo's action tonight,

34:00.451 --> 34:01.540
it's unforgivable.

34:01.541 --> 34:03.240
Each offense deserves death.

34:03.241 --> 34:05.820
Your Majesty, you mustn't
show leniency on him.

34:05.821 --> 34:07.170
If you don't execute him,

34:07.171 --> 34:09.820
are you waiting for him
to kill the entire royal family?

34:09.821 --> 34:11.041
How dare you!

34:20.741 --> 34:23.791
Should I send it to the Directorate
of the Credentials for cleansing

34:23.821 --> 34:25.311
or burn it?

34:30.381 --> 34:31.831
Keep it.

34:33.221 --> 34:34.950
Don't release it yet.

34:34.951 --> 34:36.091
Yes, Your Majesty.

34:40.261 --> 34:41.971
You have done well.

34:43.611 --> 34:46.081
Your mother has raised you well.

34:48.341 --> 34:50.751
If it weren't for tonight,

34:50.821 --> 34:51.780
I wouldn't have realized

34:51.781 --> 34:54.271
how much my uncle and brother

34:54.381 --> 34:56.641
cherish you.

34:58.131 --> 34:59.271
Father.

35:02.901 --> 35:04.681
To achieve big,

35:05.091 --> 35:07.521
one has to weigh the pros and cons.

35:08.301 --> 35:10.031
Impulse

35:10.261 --> 35:12.921
will only ruin everything.

35:15.451 --> 35:17.871
Dou Shiying incited court officials

35:18.341 --> 35:19.871
to frame princes

35:20.091 --> 35:21.911
and cause chaos in the capital.

35:22.221 --> 35:23.060
Guards.

35:23.061 --> 35:24.291
Your Majesty,

35:24.411 --> 35:25.780
I will not weigh the pros and cons

35:25.781 --> 35:27.641
or abandon innocent people
for personal gain.

35:27.861 --> 35:29.121
If you must arrest someone,

35:29.411 --> 35:30.871
I'll admit the crime.

35:31.361 --> 35:33.281
If Uncle were alive,

35:33.341 --> 35:35.391
he would never allow me

35:36.571 --> 35:38.751
to sacrifice someone important

35:38.901 --> 35:41.121
for my personal gain.

35:41.691 --> 35:42.401
This is ludicrous.

35:42.411 --> 35:44.781
How dare you pressure His Majesty
with a disgraced official?

35:44.791 --> 35:46.831
Do you have no regard for the monarch?

35:47.931 --> 35:51.041
Are you trying to continue

35:51.451 --> 35:54.751
Jiang Meisun's rebellion?

35:55.201 --> 35:56.071
What did you just say?

35:56.081 --> 35:57.780
You drew your sword
in His Majesty's presence.

35:57.781 --> 35:58.780
Are you trying
to assassinate the emperor?

35:58.781 --> 35:59.660
I'll kill you.

35:59.661 --> 36:01.391
Are you insane, Song Mo?

36:08.611 --> 36:09.751
Staying sober

36:10.531 --> 36:13.201
is a hundred times more painful
than madness.

36:14.341 --> 36:17.081
Abandoning justice for the family.

36:20.411 --> 36:23.041
You've done this more than once.

36:24.011 --> 36:26.041
Why should I still endure this?

36:26.931 --> 36:30.041
Why should I still have hope in you?

36:38.051 --> 36:39.191
Your Majesty.

36:41.861 --> 36:43.001
Your Majesty.

36:44.611 --> 36:46.081
You

36:48.261 --> 36:49.711
have always

36:52.821 --> 36:54.391
hated me.

37:09.511 --> 37:11.381
(Cultivate yourself
before governing a country)

37:15.411 --> 37:16.691
- Your Majesty!
- Your Majesty!

37:16.821 --> 37:21.570
- Your Majesty!
- Your Majesty!

37:21.571 --> 37:23.090
- Summon Official Lu!
- Your Majesty!

37:23.091 --> 37:24.360
Your Majesty!

37:24.361 --> 37:28.800
(Qianqing Palace)

37:28.801 --> 37:31.071
By the imperial decree of His Majesty,

37:31.561 --> 37:34.530
Song Mo neglected his duties,

37:34.531 --> 37:37.311
causing an incident at Changle Street.

37:37.401 --> 37:39.720
In consideration of his past merits,

37:39.721 --> 37:41.720
his death sentence is pardoned.

37:41.721 --> 37:44.181
He's stripped of all official positions

37:44.201 --> 37:46.960
and will be detained in prison

37:46.961 --> 37:49.381
for further judgment.

37:57.751 --> 38:00.221
What a shame, Duchess of Ying.

38:13.201 --> 38:14.341
Yantang!

38:16.481 --> 38:17.901
Your father is safe.

38:18.001 --> 38:19.141
Don't mind me.

38:19.401 --> 38:20.541
Don't worry.

38:21.281 --> 38:22.461
Yantang.

38:23.021 --> 38:24.161
Yantang.

38:25.511 --> 38:26.781
Yantang.

38:27.301 --> 38:29.380
♪To kiss your brow♪

38:29.381 --> 38:34.861
♪From now on,
my heart needs no disguise♪

38:35.341 --> 38:37.281
♪Wrapped in frost and snow♪

38:37.801 --> 38:38.941
Ms. Longevity!

38:39.341 --> 38:40.180
Ms. Longevity.

38:40.181 --> 38:44.851
♪Looking at this kaleidoscopic world♪

38:45.321 --> 38:46.461
Ms. Longevity.

38:49.561 --> 38:51.021
Imperial physician!

38:51.241 --> 38:52.981
Send for the imperial physician!

38:55.991 --> 39:01.461
♪Ignoring everyone's worldly advice♪

39:02.171 --> 39:04.291
♪My love is clear as the moon♪

39:05.001 --> 39:06.181
Yantang.

39:08.161 --> 39:09.301
Yantang.

39:09.721 --> 39:12.021
I must save Yantang.

39:12.721 --> 39:14.021
You can't save him.

39:14.721 --> 39:16.501
The Star of Wisdom is shining brightly.

39:16.721 --> 39:18.581
The Impulse Star is becoming dim.

39:19.001 --> 39:20.461
It's going to fall.

39:21.001 --> 39:22.360
Song Mo is nearing his death.

39:22.361 --> 39:23.440
Mr. Ji,

39:23.441 --> 39:24.720
please stop the carriage

39:24.721 --> 39:25.720
and help Madam.

39:25.721 --> 39:27.021
We can't stop.

39:27.361 --> 39:29.960
Those from the Duke of Ying's Residence
must be watching closely.

39:29.961 --> 39:32.221
We need to send Dou Zhao
to a safe place first.

39:55.561 --> 39:58.621
His Majesty is unwell and won't recover.

39:59.001 --> 40:03.261
I can only seek Buddha's blessings.

40:05.601 --> 40:09.101
(Natural Grace and Talent)

40:19.621 --> 40:21.400
Godfather, you must be very tired

40:21.401 --> 40:23.090
from the journey.

40:23.091 --> 40:26.720
According to His Majesty's decree,
I'll manage the palace

40:26.721 --> 40:29.461
and the Military Command temporarily.

40:29.561 --> 40:32.240
Godfather, just focus
on looking after His Majesty.

40:32.241 --> 40:33.821
His Majesty is ill.

40:34.281 --> 40:35.821
How could he issue an edict?

40:36.401 --> 40:37.840
Whenever His Majesty is unwell,

40:37.841 --> 40:40.360
Her Majesty will act on his behalf.

40:40.361 --> 40:41.541
Her Majesty says

40:42.041 --> 40:43.440
His Majesty

40:43.441 --> 40:45.461
needs you by his side.

40:49.761 --> 40:50.941
This way, please, Godfather.

41:03.761 --> 41:05.440
Song Mo is a court official,

41:05.441 --> 41:07.941
yet he starts the fire
and causes chaos in the palace.

41:08.041 --> 41:09.621
If he isn't executed publicly,

41:09.641 --> 41:11.061
the public wrath can't be quelled.

41:30.521 --> 41:31.901
Ji Jianming,

41:32.441 --> 41:33.821
what are you doing here?

41:35.081 --> 41:36.341
How dare you!

41:36.401 --> 41:38.261
His Highness regards me as his mentor.

41:38.681 --> 41:40.501
Who are you to call me by my name?

41:43.201 --> 41:45.101
Dou Zhao is my sister-in-law

41:45.591 --> 41:48.381
as well as the Duchess of Ying.

41:48.841 --> 41:50.261
It's natural for me

41:50.361 --> 41:51.701
to take her back.

41:51.991 --> 41:53.640
However, as an outsider,

41:53.641 --> 41:54.781
you took her away

41:55.001 --> 41:56.141
when she was unconscious.

41:58.121 --> 42:00.421
Don't think
I don't know your intentions.

42:00.761 --> 42:03.501
You abduct Dou Zhao
to control Song Mo's power.

42:03.761 --> 42:05.021
You're the one

42:05.401 --> 42:06.621
with ulterior intentions.

42:10.391 --> 42:13.380
Don't think you can escape
after disrupting Lord Qing's plan.

42:13.381 --> 42:15.621
If His Highness finds out
you saved someone he hates,

42:15.881 --> 42:17.021
he will kill you.

42:20.001 --> 42:22.821
When did His Highness ever order you
to target the Duchess?

42:23.641 --> 42:27.221
You've rushed here even before Song Mo's
sentence was issued.

42:28.001 --> 42:31.261
Do you think His Highness
won't notice your intentions?

42:34.121 --> 42:35.661
Intentions or not,

42:36.001 --> 42:37.461
we'll find out.

42:37.481 --> 42:38.621
Search the place!

42:58.841 --> 43:00.120
This Resentment

43:00.121 --> 43:01.720
will bring you excruciating pain.

43:01.721 --> 43:05.421
Take your time and savor the pain.

43:05.561 --> 43:06.701
Yantang.

43:07.081 --> 43:08.221
Yantang.

43:08.481 --> 43:09.621
Yantang.

43:10.111 --> 43:11.560
Madam!

43:11.561 --> 43:13.131
Don't scare me, Madam!

43:13.481 --> 43:17.921
♪The pain of goodbye?♪

43:18.201 --> 43:21.381
♪If dreams are shattered,
can they be whole again?♪

43:21.961 --> 43:25.541
♪If today brings hope, will it stay?♪

43:25.641 --> 43:31.541
♪Will the pain
just weave itself deeper?♪

43:31.881 --> 43:33.200
♪Where can this restless heart
find peace?♪

43:33.201 --> 43:36.280
♪Left alone in an empty hall♪

43:36.281 --> 43:40.141
♪A lifetime chasing fate's lonely call♪

43:40.201 --> 43:44.440
♪Watching seasons fade and storms rise♪

43:44.441 --> 43:47.000
♪It hurts but it's not all for nothing♪

43:47.001 --> 43:48.280
♪My heart is as empty as a quiet street♪

43:48.281 --> 43:51.320
♪Who cares about the path I walk alone?♪

43:51.321 --> 43:55.480
♪Would you take away
the weight of the past?♪

43:55.481 --> 43:57.480
♪Life is fleeting, like morning frost♪

43:57.481 --> 44:00.680
♪Even a moment feels endless with you♪

44:00.681 --> 44:06.821
♪Like a stream flowing steady
through time♪

44:08.801 --> 44:15.701
♪A lone flower falls from the eaves
Moonlight graces steps beneath♪

44:16.161 --> 44:23.381
♪Can anyone ease the pain of goodbye?♪

44:23.681 --> 44:26.901
♪If dreams are shattered,
can they be whole again?♪

44:27.481 --> 44:31.061
♪If today brings hope, will it stay?♪

44:31.161 --> 44:37.061
♪Will the pain
just weave itself deeper?♪

44:37.681 --> 44:38.960
♪In this chaotic world♪

44:38.961 --> 44:41.920
♪Only love lasts♪

44:41.921 --> 44:45.661
♪We'll get through every challenge
together♪

44:45.841 --> 44:50.080
♪No matter how cold or uncertain
the road♪

44:50.081 --> 44:52.680
♪There's nothing to fear
when I'm with you♪

44:52.681 --> 44:53.880
♪My heart feels empty♪

44:53.881 --> 44:56.800
♪But I can hear your voice♪

44:56.801 --> 45:01.080
♪In this life,
under moonlight and across the oceans♪

45:01.081 --> 45:03.501
♪We’ll find our way back to each other♪

45:03.801 --> 45:04.640
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama)

45:04.641 --> 45:05.520
(Every medical behaviour involved
and medicine used in the drama)

45:05.521 --> 45:06.480
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home)

45:06.481 --> 45:12.741
♪Together,
we’ll make every moment count♪
